Authentication Endpoints
        POST /auth/register - Register new user (default role: STUDENT)

        POST /auth/login - Login user

        POST /auth/refresh - Refresh access token

        GET /auth/profile - Get current user profile (protected)


User Management Endpoints (Protected)
        POST /users - Create user (Admin only)

        GET /users - Get all users (Admin only)

        GET /users/instructors - Get all instructors

        GET /users/students - Get all students

        GET /users/profile - Get own profile

        PATCH /users/profile - Update own profile

        POST /users/profile/avatar - Upload avatar

        POST /users/profile/change-password - Change password

        GET /users/role/:roleId - Get users by role (Admin only)

        GET /users/:id - Get user by ID (Admin only)

        PATCH /users/:id - Update user (Admin only)

        DELETE /users/:id - Delete user (Admin only)      


Course Endpoints
                POST /courses - Create course (Instructor/Admin)

                GET /courses - Get all courses (public: published only, auth: all)

                GET /courses/instructor/:instructorId - Get instructor's courses

                GET /courses/category/:category - Get courses by category

                GET /courses/analytics/:id - Get course analytics (Instructor/Admin)

                GET /courses/:id - Get course details

                PATCH /courses/:id - Update course (Instructor/Admin)

                DELETE /courses/:id - Delete course (Instructor/Admin)

                POST /courses/:id/publish - Publish course (Instructor/Admin)

                POST /courses/:id/unpublish - Unpublish course (Instructor/Admin)

                POST /courses/:id/thumbnail - Upload thumbnail (Instructor/Admin)  


Lesson Endpoints
                POST /courses/:courseId/lessons - Create lesson (Instructor/Admin)

                GET /courses/:courseId/lessons - Get course lessons

                GET /courses/:courseId/lessons/:id - Get lesson details

                PATCH /courses/:courseId/lessons/:id - Update lesson (Instructor/Admin)

                DELETE /courses/:courseId/lessons/:id - Delete lesson (Instructor/Admin)

                POST /courses/:courseId/lessons/reorder - Reorder lessons (Instructor/Admin)



Resource Endpoints
                POST /lessons/:lessonId/resources - Upload resource (Instructor/Admin)

                GET /lessons/:lessonId/resources - Get lesson resources

                GET /lessons/:lessonId/resources/:id - Get resource details

                DELETE /lessons/:lessonId/resources/:id - Delete resource (Instructor/Admin)                





Enrollment Endpoints
                POST /enrollments - Enroll in a course (Student only)

                GET /enrollments - Get all enrollments (role-based filtering)

                GET /enrollments/my-enrollments - Get current student's enrollments

                GET /enrollments/student/:studentId - Get enrollments by student (Admin/Instructor)

                GET /enrollments/course/:courseId - Get enrollments by course (Admin/Instructor)

                GET /enrollments/stats - Get enrollment statistics (Admin/Instructor)

                GET /enrollments/student/:studentId/progress-summary - Get student progress summary

                GET /enrollments/:id - Get enrollment details

                GET /enrollments/:id/progress - Get enrollment progress

                POST /enrollments/:id/lessons/:lessonId/complete - Mark lesson as completed

                PATCH /enrollments/:id/progress - Update progress

                PATCH /enrollments/:id/status - Update enrollment status (Admin/Instructor)

                DELETE /enrollments/:id - Delete enrollment (Admin only)